                    "text": "Phở is more than just a dish; it’s a cultural experience. This aromatic noodle soup features a rich broth made from simmered beef or chicken bones, fragrant herbs, and spices. Topped with fresh herbs, bean sprouts, lime, and chili, Phở is enjoyed at any time of the day and is a must-try for any food lover."
