                    "title": "Bánh Xèo (Vietnamese Pancakes)",
                    "text": "Bánh Xèo, or Vietnamese pancakes, are savory delights made from rice flour, turmeric, and coconut milk, filled with a mix of shrimp, pork, bean sprouts, and onions. The pancakes are crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, served with fresh herbs and a tangy dipping sauce. They are a popular choice for lunch or dinner."
